{"data":[{"id":"1708516869147330","contents":"# 쉬운 SDK 설치 및 개발 환경 \r\n- 다양한 개발 언어의 개발 도구에 대한 쉬운 설치 및 활용법 소개 ","height":66,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":true,"type":"mrk","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true},{"id":"1708407645172459","contents":"## nodejs 개발 환경 설치 및 활용 \n[https://docs.machbase.com/kr/dbms/sdk-integration/nodejs](https://docs.machbase.com/kr/dbms/sdk-integration/nodejs)\n\n[https://www.npmjs.com/package/@machbase/ts-client](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@machbase/ts-client)\n```\nnpm install @machbase/ts-client\n```\n```bash\nsjkim@CEO-PC:~$  npm install @machbase/ts-client\n\nadded 3 packages in 3s\nnpm notice\nnpm notice New minor version of npm available! 11.8.0 -> 11.13.0\nnpm notice Changelog: https://github.com/npm/cli/releases/tag/v11.13.0\nnpm notice To update run: npm install -g npm@11.13.0\nnpm notice\nsjkim@CEO-PC:~$ \n```\n\n### 소스코드\n```js\n// quickstart.js (CommonJS, Node 18+)\nconst { createConnection } = require('@machbase/ts-client');\n\nasync function main() {\n  const conn = createConnection({ host: '127.0.0.1', user: 'SYS', password: 'MANAGER', port: 5657 });\n  await conn.connect();\n\n  const [rows] = await conn.query('SELECT * FROM v$tables ORDER BY NAME LIMIT ?', [10]);\n  console.table(rows);\n\n  await conn.end();\n}\n\nmain().catch(err => console.error('Unexpected failure:', err));\n```\n### 결과\n```bash\nsjkim@CEO-PC:~/node_modules/@machbase/ts-client/src/example-js$ node conn.js\n┌─────────┬─────────────────────┬──────┬─────────────┬──────────┬─────────┬──────────┬──────┐\n│ (index) │ NAME                │ TYPE │ DATABASE_ID │ ID       │ USER_ID │ COLCOUNT │ FLAG │\n├─────────┼─────────────────────┼──────┼─────────────┼──────────┼─────────┼──────────┼──────┤\n│ 0       │ 'V$CACHE'           │ 1    │ -1n         │ 1000027n │ 0       │ 3        │ 0    │\n│ 1       │ 'V$CACHE_OBJECTS'   │ 1    │ -1n         │ 1000028n │ 0       │ 5        │ 0    │\n│ 2       │ 'V$COLUMNS'         │ 1    │ -1n         │ 1000056n │ 0       │ 14       │ 0    │\n│ 3       │ 'V$HTTP_STATUS'     │ 1    │ -1n         │ 1000017n │ 0       │ 11       │ 0    │\n│ 4       │ 'V$LICENSE_INFO'    │ 1    │ -1n         │ 1000012n │ 0       │ 11       │ 0    │\n│ 5       │ 'V$MUTEX'           │ 1    │ -1n         │ 1000004n │ 0       │ 18       │ 0    │\n│ 6       │ 'V$MUTEX_WAIT_STAT' │ 1    │ -1n         │ 1000011n │ 0       │ 6        │ 0    │\n│ 7       │ 'V$NEO_SESSION'     │ 1    │ -1n         │ 1000018n │ 0       │ 7        │ 0    │\n│ 8       │ 'V$NEO_STMT'        │ 1    │ -1n         │ 1000019n │ 0       │ 8        │ 0    │\n│ 9       │ 'V$PROPERTY'        │ 1    │ -1n         │ 1000003n │ 0       │ 8        │ 0    │\n└─────────┴─────────────────────┴──────┴─────────────┴──────────┴─────────┴──────────┴──────┘\n```\n","height":272,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":true,"type":"mrk","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true},{"id":"1777427043669188","contents":"## python3(pip3) 개발 환경 설치 및 활용 \r\n[https://docs.machbase.com/kr/dbms/sdk-integration/python/](https://docs.machbase.com/kr/dbms/sdk-integration/python/)\r\n\r\n[https://pypi.org/project/machbaseapi/](https://pypi.org/project/machbaseapi/)\r\n```\r\npip3 install machbaseapi\r\n```\r\n```bash\r\n(.venv) hermes@CEO-PC:~$ pip3 install machbaseapi\r\nCollecting machbaseapi\r\n  Downloading machbaseapi-2.2-py3-none-any.whl.metadata (6.6 kB)\r\nDownloading machbaseapi-2.2-py3-none-any.whl (21 kB)\r\nInstalling collected packages: machbaseapi\r\nSuccessfully installed machbaseapi-2.2\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 소스코드 : conntest.py\r\n```js\r\n#******************************************************************************\r\n# Copyright of this product 2013-2023,\r\n# MACHBASE Corporation(or Inc.) or its subsidiaries.\r\n# All Rights reserved.\r\n#******************************************************************************\r\n\r\nimport os\r\nfrom machbaseAPI.machbaseAPI import machbase\r\n\r\ndef connect():\r\n    port = int(os.environ['MACHBASE_PORT_NO'])\r\n    db = machbase()\r\n    if db.open('127.0.0.1','SYS','MANAGER',port) == 0 :\r\n        return db.result()\r\n\r\n    if db.execute('select count(*) from m$tables') == 0 :\r\n        return db.result()\r\n\r\n    result = db.result()\r\n\r\n    if db.close() == 0 :\r\n        return db.result()\r\n\r\n    return result\r\n\r\nif __name__==\"__main__\":\r\n    print(connect())\r\n\r\n```\r\n### 결과\r\n```bash\r\nsjkim4@CEO-PC:~/tmp$ python3 ./conntest.py\r\n{\"count(*)\":\"13\"}\r\nsjkim4@CEO-PC:~/tmp$\r\n```\r\n","height":296,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":true,"type":"mrk","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true},{"id":"1777428271156465","contents":"## DotNet Connector  개발 환경 설치 및 활용 \r\n[https://docs.machbase.com/kr/dbms/sdk-integration/dotnet/](https://docs.machbase.com/kr/dbms/sdk-integration/dotnet/)\r\n\r\n[https://www.nuget.org/packages/UniMachNetConnector](https://www.nuget.org/packages/UniMachNetConnector)\r\n```\r\ndotnet add package UniMachNetConnector --version 8.0.53\r\ndotnet build\r\n```\r\n```bash\r\nsjkim@CEO-PC:~/work/nfx/test/regress/dotnet/160-disconnect$ dotnet build\r\nmsbuild 버전 17.8.49+7806cbf7b(.NET용)\r\n  Determining projects to restore...\r\n  All projects are up-to-date for restore.\r\n  160-disconnect -> /home/sjkim/work/nfx/test/regress/dotnet/160-disconnect/bin/Debug/net5.0/160-disconnect.dll\r\n\r\n빌드했습니다.\r\n    경고 0개\r\n    오류 0개\r\n\r\n경과 시간: 00:00:03.54\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 소스코드 : 160-disconnect.cs\r\n```\r\n<Project Sdk=\"Microsoft.NET.Sdk\">\r\n\r\n  <PropertyGroup>\r\n    <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\r\n    <TargetFramework>net5.0</TargetFramework>\r\n    <RollForward>Major</RollForward>\r\n     <NoWarn>NETSDK1138</NoWarn>\r\n    <RootNamespace>_160_disconnect</RootNamespace>\r\n  </PropertyGroup>\r\n\r\n  <ItemGroup>\r\n    <PackageReference Include=\"UniMachNetConnector\" Version=\"8.0.53\" />\r\n  </ItemGroup>\r\n\r\n</Project>\r\n```\r\n\r\n```cs\r\nusing Mach.Data.MachClient;\r\n\r\nnamespace _160_disconnect\r\n{\r\n    class Program\r\n    {\r\n        public const string SERVER = \"127.0.0.1\";\r\n        public static int PORT_NO = 5656;\t\r\n        public const string UID = \"SYS\";\r\n        public const string PWD = \"manager\";\r\n        static void Main(string[] args)\r\n        {\r\n\t    PORT_NO = int.Parse(args[0]);\r\n            MachConnection conn = new MachConnection($\"SERVER={SERVER};PORT_NO={PORT_NO};UID={UID};PWD={PWD}\");\r\n            conn.Open();\r\n            Console.WriteLine(\"Connection Open.\");\r\n            MachCommand comm = new MachCommand(\"select id, name, value from v$sysstat where name like '%DISCONNECT%' order by value desc limit 1\", conn);\r\n            MachDataReader reader = comm.ExecuteReader();\r\n            Console.WriteLine(\"=============================\");\r\n            while(reader.Read())\r\n            {\r\n                Console.WriteLine($\"{reader.GetInt32(0)} {reader.GetString(1)} {reader.GetInt64(2)}\");\r\n            }\r\n            Console.WriteLine(\"=============================\");\r\n            conn.Close();\r\n            Console.WriteLine(\"Connection Close!\");\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n```\r\n### 결과\r\n```bash\r\nsjkim@CEO-PC:~/work/nfx/test/regress/dotnet/160-disconnect$ dotnet run 5656\r\nConnection Open.\r\n=============================\r\n1 DISCONNECT_CNT 17438\r\n=============================\r\nConnection Close!\r\n\r\n```\r\n","height":478,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":true,"type":"mrk","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true},{"id":"1777429003635474","contents":"## Go  개발 환경 설치 및 활용 \r\n[https://docs.machbase.com/kr/dbms/sdk-integration/go/](https://docs.machbase.com/kr/dbms/sdk-integration/go/)\r\n\r\n[https://github.com/machbase/neo-client](https://github.com/machbase/neo-client)\r\n\r\n```\r\n go get github.com/machbase/neo-client@latest\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 소스코드 : gotest.go\r\n```go\r\npackage main\r\n\r\nimport (\r\n    \"context\"\r\n    \"fmt\"\r\n    \"log\"\r\n    \"time\"\r\n\r\n    \"github.com/machbase/neo-client/api\"\r\n    \"github.com/machbase/neo-client/machgo\"\r\n)\r\n\r\nfunc main() {\r\n    conf := &machgo.Config{\r\n        Host:         \"127.0.0.1\",\r\n        Port:         5656,\r\n        MaxOpenConn:  -1,\r\n        MaxOpenQuery: -1,\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    mdb, err := machgo.NewDatabase(conf)\r\n    if err != nil {\r\n        log.Fatal(err)\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    ctx := context.Background()\r\n    conn, err := mdb.Connect(ctx, api.WithPassword(\"sys\", \"manager\"))\r\n    if err != nil {\r\n        log.Fatal(err)\r\n    }\r\n    defer conn.Close()\r\n\r\n    result := conn.Exec(ctx, `\r\n        CREATE TAG TABLE IF NOT EXISTS sample_data (\r\n            name VARCHAR(100) PRIMARY KEY,\r\n            time DATETIME BASETIME,\r\n            value DOUBLE\r\n        )\r\n    `)\r\n    if err := result.Err(); err != nil {\r\n        log.Fatal(err)\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    for i := 0; i < 5; i++ {\r\n        result := conn.Exec(\r\n            ctx,\r\n            `INSERT INTO sample_data VALUES (?, ?, ?)`,\r\n            fmt.Sprintf(\"sensor_%d\", i),\r\n            time.Now(),\r\n            float64(i)*1.5,\r\n        )\r\n        if err := result.Err(); err != nil {\r\n            log.Fatal(err)\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    rows, err := conn.Query(ctx, \r\n        `SELECT name, time, value FROM sample_data ORDER BY time`)\r\n    if err != nil {\r\n        log.Fatal(err)\r\n    }\r\n    defer rows.Close()\r\n\r\n    for rows.Next() {\r\n        var name string\r\n        var tm time.Time\r\n        var value float64\r\n\r\n        if err := rows.Scan(&name, &tm, &value); err != nil {\r\n            log.Fatal(err)\r\n        }\r\n        fmt.Printf(\"Name: %s, Time: %s, Value: %.2f\\n\",\r\n            name, tm.Local().Format(time.RFC3339), value)\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n","height":311,"lineHeight":19,"minimal":true,"type":"mrk","tqlType":null,"lang":[["markdown","Markdown"],["SQL","SQL"],["go","TQL"],["shell","Shell"]],"result":"","status":true}]}